I realize that there is a notification process that will send an email to those associated to an issue if there has been modifications to that issue.

My question, is there a way to highlight or signify in the Queues display when an issue has been updated/modified?

Currently, the process requires me to go through all of my emails to see if something has been added to an issue, it would be great if I could just look at the Queue display to see if an issue has been flagged as modified.

