With the recent introduction in Service Desk of KB related articles being displayed when an agent is working on a ticket, it occurred to me that the main limitation of this otherwise great new feature is that the Service Desk KB is primarily aimed at customers, particularly since the KB must either be public or the user accounts must match Confluence.

For agents, it may be typical (as in our case), that there are multiple spaces - one that is customer-facing and one that is agent-facing. It would be great if Service Desk could be extended to support that scenario so that when an agent is working on a ticket, agent-related articles can be bubbled up on the display or searched for from the existing UI.

